## PR checklist (navigation / filters / tabs)

- [ ] Shareable state written to URL on every code path that changes the view
- [ ] F5 restores the same view
- [ ] Browser Back returns to previous view without stale UI
- [ ] Share/copy link matches visible view
- [ ] No full-page loading flash on intra-route param change
- [ ] `routing.mdc` updated if path or query contract changed
- [ ] No large data in `history.state`
